{
  "stem": "8916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were moved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We moved into a smaller area and then finally ended up living in an attic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother and I ended up living in an attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it's very difficult to say by this time, because it was so-- so unreal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there for three or four months in the attic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the ghetto was split in half, and one of the-- one of the-- part of the ghetto was going to be eliminated, we lived on the-- on that side.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so everyone who still lived on that side had to get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I remember the last thing my mother did was that she got a pot and-- and left, and got out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But got out very late, the last minute, with this pot in her hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's-- that's the question everybody asks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you doing with this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it came in handy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She knew what she was doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she would make-- boil potatoes and make soup and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, she--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was the kind of person that was very good under pressure, in the immediate emergency.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did all these things in the emergency.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was the last one to leave, and she would pick up something, and somebody would say, oh, leave that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then next-- next time, we needed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So finally-- but when the pressure was off, she'd just come apart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, She would be practically hysterical about what was going to happen and what happened to-- to my older brother, and what happened to-- where is Aviva, and all these things that just came pouring out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somewhat.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, I only came to this understanding later, to this-- to this better understanding.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
